# PyEasy

A tiny library to make Python easier and friendlier for beginners.

## Installation

```bash
pip install pyeasyal
```

## Usage

```python
from pyeasy import say_hello, ask

say_hello("Ali")
name = ask("What's your name?")
print(f"Welcome, {name}!")
```
